/p>\n<ul><li>rust-analyzer(必装)</li><li>Better TOML(推荐)</li><li>crates(推荐)</li><li>Error Lens(推荐)</li></ul>\n</div>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/editerView/markdown_views-22a2fefd3b.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/style-4f8fbf9108.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n</div>", "first_tag": "C++", "cpp": 1, "csharp": 0, "python": 0, "javascript": 0, "java": 0, "sql": 0, "php": 0, "time": "2022-07-11 18:42:13", "summary": "安装、配置开发环境安装这里不过多赘述。如果安装成功，将出现下面这行：编译工具：上安装需要有环境，有两种方式可供选择：官方推荐在安装时可自行选择。配置开发环境推荐作为的开发工具下载地址：插件：必装推荐推"}